{"tid":150022,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"談本多忠勝","createTime":"2017-03-09T16:58:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T13:39:26.000Z","uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75033a099684e3ede7b23d369a450205821be40f","tid":150022,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:58:22.000Z","msg":"本多忠勝係邊個？<br />\n其實我都唔知道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果本多終勝<br />\n唔知你又會點睇<br />\n<br />\n當你嘅資本夠多<br />\n最終點都會贏番<br />\n<br />\n就好似買樓放租<br />\n十年廿年三十年<br />\n點都會返番哂黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係如果冇資本<br />\n連諗嘅資格都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n又或者可以咁講<br />\n資本等於嘗試機會<br />\n例如有錢人仔女同<br />\n窮撚仔女都去創業<br />\n<br />\n有錢人可以試好多好多次<br />\n直到成功為止，最後贏番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n窮撚就連一次都輸唔起<br />\n失敗一鋪就Game over<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n本多終勝？鬼唔知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能你覺得係老生常談、<br />\n啊媽係女人嘅廢嗡⋯⋯<br />\n垃圾窮撚對現實嘅抱怨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係我唔係想抱怨啲咩<br />\n我都信我命由我不由天<br />\n我都想用自己雙手改變命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後，問題關鍵黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬會戶口得番廿蚊<br />\n買咩好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ba67168be81209412bf9f19a049c73c31dee0e8","tid":150022,"uid":10011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:59:26.000Z","msg":"本多終勝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0434da286ac224fc44070fb2de04342311e9e35a","tid":150022,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:12:06.000Z","msg":"離題 0分"},{"pid":"44d2054420d01205fcd9f76a071ea7eb2781f2eb","tid":150022,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:20:05.000Z","msg":"比次機會我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fcc050c337be7d28d83427071feea9e31b3adc","tid":150022,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比次機會我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬會個莊真係本多終勝<br />\n我諗你呢20$都係凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n安德烈治大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申無買因為昨天馬仔輸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828e4019ac74f8ae1a0ea7535b08bf466e73847e","tid":150022,"uid":31777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比次機會我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬會個莊真係本多終勝<br />\n我諗你呢20$都係凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n安德烈治大波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申無買因為昨天馬仔輸晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔該哂巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。輸都唔緊要<br />\n我就係一個成功嘅窮撚例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係好事定壞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b91e1d8c605a7e9f41b8eb46e6fa2bf83aae456","tid":150022,"uid":6044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T19:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>比次機會我啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n馬會個莊真係本多終勝<br />\n我諗你呢20$都係凍過水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />